column5: Well, It's finally warming up, Mista W got a little ice fishing done on Thursday... Not one walleye to be had, sauger city but mmmm mmmm good. Nice eaters. Going to try Howey Bay today.. I see a few shacks set up accross from my place.. Must be catchin' something.. I'll have to try my secret summer hole...Hope there's no locals reading my post...They'll be out there for sure.. hehe.. Happy fishing... Mista W
Slip up to Chukuni....50 per hour anytime of the day....he he he
